Liverpool midfielder Philippe Coutinho has been nominated for the PFA Player and Young Player of the Year awards . 
  The Reds face Aston Villa in the FA Cup semi-final at Wembley on Sunday . 
  Coutinho met Brazil legend Pele for the first time last month . 
  He described it as the 'ultimate honour' to speak to Pele . 
  Liverpool face Manchester United in the Premier League on Saturday . 
 